Readme2Web v1.0 // 2008-08-11

  sow readme2web [output]

Generates a basic website based on a README
file. It does this by sectioning the README
into tabs based on <h2>'s.

If output is not given, generates to the first
location it finds called website, web or site,
in the project's root directory. Defaults to
'web' if none is found.

